caption: Close up view of an old yellow Mercedes Benz on a lawn, surrounded by other vehicles and trees
orig: 一辆在草坪上的黄色旧款式奔驰车近景，周围有其他车辆和树木

caption: In an old church, a man in a suit is standing and looking at the camera with flowers in his hands.
orig: 在一座老教堂里，一位身着西装的男士正手捧鲜花站着看向镜头

caption: Half-length shot of a man holding flowers while standing in a church, surrounded by wooden fences, stairs and statues
orig: 一位男士拿着手捧花站在教堂内的半身照，周围是木制结构的围栏、楼梯和雕像

orig: 在白色前面和白色床上用品的背景下，一位女士戴着帽子和眼镜、身穿露肩上衣、露着双腿看向左侧的写真

caption: A full body close-up of an Asian lady wearing a black woolen hat and black-rimmed glasses is sitting on a white bed sheet with a white wall background. She is only wearing a black top and looking sideways.
orig: 白墙背景白色床单上座着一位头戴黑色毛线帽黑边框眼镜只穿黑色上衣侧头看的亚洲裔女士全身特写

caption: A photo of two ladies in front of the store. The lady on the left is smiling and looking at the camera. The lady on the right is looking to the right and is blurry.
orig: 店铺前两位女士的合照，左边的女士微笑着看向镜头，右边的女士看着右侧而且很模糊

caption: Close up shot of two women in summer clothes walking on the street by the roadside, one is smiling and the other is looking sideways, surrounded by shop roller shutters, panoramic view of a man and the shop
orig: 两位穿着夏装的女士在路边的街道上的近照，有一位在微笑另一位在侧头看，周围有店铺卷帘门，一位男士和店铺的全景

caption: Standing under the grape trellis and looking up, you can see many green grapes growing among the green leaves.
orig: 站在葡萄架下抬头向上看，能看到绿叶中长着很多绿葡萄

caption: A close-up view of a vineyard with bunches of grapes hanging on the rack and green leaves as background
orig: 架子上挂满了一串串的葡萄并有绿叶陪衬的一片葡萄园近景

caption: Behind the neatly arranged kitchen utensils, my eyes looked towards the left corner where a uniformed female chef was holding a basin of ingredients on the table.
orig: 在整齐摆放着厨具的后，眼睛看向左侧角落一位身穿制服的女厨师手里端着放在桌子上的一盆食材

caption: Close-up shot of a woman in black chef uniform carrying a rectangular stainless steel basin filled with meat, surrounded by a kitchen background with many kitchen utensils and storage bowls
orig: 一位穿着黑色厨师服的女士正在端着一个长方形不锈钢装满肉的盆子的近照，周围是厨房背景有很多厨具和收纳餐盆

caption: Close-up of a little bird standing on a branch. Its head and wings are black, its belly is yellow, and its two paws are red. The background of the picture is blurry.
orig: 站在树枝上的一只小鸟的特写，它的头和翅膀都是黑色，腹部为黄色，两只爪子是红色的，画面背景很模糊

caption: Close-up of a kingfisher standing on a branch with a blurry green background
orig: 一只站在树枝上的翠鸟的特写，背景是模糊的绿色

caption: From the perspective of the black and white photo, there are many stone steps in the woods
orig: 黑白照片视角下，树林中有很多石头做成的台阶

caption: Close up shot of black and white stone staircase with circular design surrounded by woods
orig: 树林围绕的圆形设计石梯的黑白近景

caption: Standing on the mountain and looking down, you can see the sun shining on some stone ruins, surrounded by dense woods.
orig: 站在山上向下俯视能看到阳光照耀着一些用石头筑起来的遗迹，旁边是茂密的树林

caption: Panoramic view of the natural landscape of lawns, stone steps, woods and lakes
orig: 草坪，石阶，树林，湖面的自然景观全景

orig: 阳光照耀下，两只猴子在泥土空地上蹲坐在石块上，左边的猴子比右边的体型大，他们都是浅灰色的毛

orig: 在一张垫着绿色桌布的玻璃桌上放着一个白色的盘子，盘子里装着很多煎饺

orig: 一盘放在玻璃桌上的中式煎饺的特写

caption: When you stand on a high floor of a building and look down, you can see many windows.

orig: 一座现代公寓大楼的正面斜着拍的照片，有很多方形的窗户

orig: 蓝天白云背景下阳光照耀着，站在空地上抬头看对面的典型欧式建筑，建筑物两旁都站着一些树木

orig: 阳光照耀下站在山坡下的泥土空地上四个人站成一排微笑看向镜头，从左边数第二位是女性，其他三位都是男性

caption: Group photo of three men and one woman in the wild, with mountains, green plants and barbed wire in the background
orig: 三男一女在野外的合影，背景是大山和绿植，铁丝网

caption: Woman in bikini standing and drinking beer at yacht party
orig: 游艇派对上站着，在喝啤酒，穿着比基尼的女人

caption: Under the scorching sun, several girls on the boat were drinking. One of them was blowing on a bottle, and the other was wearing sunglasses and praying.
orig: 烈日当空，船上的几名姑娘在喝酒，其中一名正对瓶吹，另外一名戴着墨镜祈祷

caption: The rear of a white Lamborghini in front of the house
orig: 屋前的一辆白色兰博基尼车尾

orig: 一辆白色跑车尾部近景图，车牌号ej984mh, 旁边有木屋

caption: Two male marathon runners who were sweating profusely while being watched on the track.
orig: 在跑道中被围观，跑得满头大汗的两名马拉松男性跑手

orig: 两名男子正奋力向前奔跑，两旁是给他俩加油的人群

caption: A boy doing a ppt presentation in the classroom
orig: 教室里正在做ppt简报的男生

caption: A man is giving a report to his colleagues in a conference room with a projector behind him
orig: 一名男子正在会议室给同事做汇报，后面有投影仪

caption: Display of antique toy cars in toy store
orig: 玩具店里的古董玩具车陈列

caption: Classic toy cars are displayed on a shelf with three levels, one on each level, and other cars next to the shelf.
orig: 摆放的古典玩具车，一个架子有3层，每层放一辆，架子旁边还有其他车

orig: 夜间海边一个回头微笑的金发女人

caption: Black and white photo, a plump white woman wearing a floral skirt is looking back and smiling
orig: 黑白照，一名穿碎花裙丰满的白人女子正回眸一笑

caption: A large piece of salmon meat on the cutting board
orig: 砧板上一大片三文鱼肉

orig: 棕色桌子白色案板上切好的三文鱼，旁边还有一把刀

orig: 公司里两个在握手的黑人

orig: 办公室里的三名黑皮肤男士，两名正在单手相握回头看镜头微笑，另一只手在传递资料

orig: 一对夫妇手拉手走过来，男的穿西装戴眼镜，女的穿宝蓝色礼服，开怀大笑

orig: 在等过马路，穿着制服的南亚军人和后面三个路人

orig: 破旧的街道公交车站牌旁站着4个阿拉伯男人，白衣男子和黑衣男子在交谈，戴帽子的男子站在前面挡住另一名男子，栅栏外有一辆破车

orig: 峡谷间干枯的岩石和沙地

orig: 仅填了两朵花，其余都留白的填色作业纸

orig: 农村城市里的一条街道，旁边的商铺和停在街上的车

orig: 在开着灯光的杂货铺门口，能看到摆着各种各样的杂货，一位男士站在门口看着镜头微笑

orig: 一位穿着白色背心的男士站在一个墙上挂有中世纪油画的屋子里，背对着镜头看另一面墙上的标语

A man in a white vest stands next to the screen and reads the words above. There is an arch next to the screen. The door is blocked by three chains.
orig: 博物馆内部，左边墙上有一幅画，画上有5个人，右边墙壁上有蓝白屏幕，上面有文字介绍，一个穿白背心的男人站在屏幕旁看上面的字，屏幕旁有一个拱形门，门口用三根铁链挡住

orig: 一架饭店的院子里放着很多桌椅，有白色遮阳伞，还有绿色盆栽

orig: 中世纪以呼吁人民反抗为主题的油画，一位白衣女性右手拿号角左手举起红旗，旁边有很多人手里拿着长枪

orig: 工厂车间里三个横放的黑色钢罐，近处的钢罐尾部有一架梯子，最里面的钢罐上面蹲着一个男人，地上有横七竖八的线，彩钢顶棚

orig: 在一间红砖砌筑起来的室内，一位戴着白色假发的男士站在一个白板面前，并一只手拿着上面的白纸，能看到白纸上用红笔写这英文

caption: There are three people in the room. At the front is a white-haired man wearing jeans and a light blue T-shirt. His hair is long and curly. His left hand is flipping a page on a stand. Behind him is a man holding a simple drawing in his hand. There are also people in the distance. there is a woman
orig: 室内3个人，最前面是一个穿牛仔裤浅蓝t恤的白发男人，头发又长又卷，左手正在翻支架上的一页纸，后面站着一个手捧简易图纸片的人，远处还有一个女人

orig: 在河水里游着的醍醐嘴里叼起一条鱼的特写

orig: 一只鸬鹚正在水面捕鱼，鸬鹚张开嘴，嘴旁边露出一个鱼头

orig: 在一片小河滩上停靠着一辆木船，远处是低矮的房屋、绿草和山脉

orig: 水面上的一条旧木船，船很大，上面有一个男人，还有方形的船舱，水又混又黄，岸边有茅屋，远处有田野和绿树

orig: 乌云下的泰国寺庙景观，在马路边上的草丛后面，是一片典型的泰式风格的寺庙

The street lights are on, illuminating the temple in a magnificent way. There are red flowers blooming in the flower bed, and there are low Short trees and hedges
orig: 傍晚的佛教寺庙，一栋是红色的墙壁和屋顶，一座白墙黑顶塔，天空中有厚厚的云层，路灯亮了，把寺庙照的金碧辉煌，花坛里有盛开的红色鲜花，还有低矮的树和绿篱

orig: 蓝天白云下碧绿的水面，远处有茂密的绿树

orig: 白色背景下一个老式且有点生锈的门锁

orig: 白色背景上的一个金属横锁，锁身正中心有一个黑色方框，上面有十字形

orig: 在树上坐着的松鼠

caption: A fat squirrel sits on a tree with thick roots and green leaves around it
orig: 一只胖松鼠坐在树上，粗粗的树根，周围绿色树叶

orig: 士兵后面还有其他士兵以及普通人民

caption: A soldier in camouflage uniform and black hat faces the camera, surrounded by four men and with houses and mountains in the distance
orig: 一名穿迷彩服戴黑帽子的士兵面对镜头，周围有4个男人，远处有房子和山

orig: 秋天时夕阳下无人的公园

orig: 大广场中心的路，路两边是草坪和路灯，草坪里还有树，远处有楼房和晨曦

orig: 屋顶上装着生锈的波浪形铁板

caption: Red tiles on the roof and green trees behind the house
orig: 屋顶红色的瓦片，屋后有绿树

caption: A notification letter with a red seal
orig: 一张盖着红印章的通知函

caption: China Unicom’s number arrears notification letter dated December 14, 2010
orig: 2010年12月14日中国联通的号码欠费通知函

caption: Buildings under construction on the side of the highway with many cars

orig: 厨房里两个锅正在烧菜，其中一个盖着盖子，里面是黄色状食物，另一个没有盖的在炖汤

caption: On the stove, there is a pot with a glass lid, and there is egg yolk-like food inside. There is a spoon outside the pot next to it, and there is a spatula in the black pot in the distance. What food is being cooked?
orig: 灶台上，有一只锅盖着玻璃盖，里面有蛋黄一样的食物，旁边锅外面有一只勺子，远处黑色的锅里有一只铲子，正在煮什么食物

caption: Under the blue sky, standing in the green space, you can see at a glance a pyramid shape carved out of loess.
orig: 蓝蓝的天空下，站在绿地里，一眼望过去是黄土雕刻出来的金字塔形状

caption: Blue sky, white clouds and green grass, a pyramid-like architectural ruins in the wild. The stones are reddish brown, with green grass on them, neatly repaired and surrounded by trees.
orig: 蓝天白云碧草，野外一处像金字塔一样的建筑遗址，石块呈红褐色，上面有绿草，修葺整齐，周围有树

caption: In front of a market vendor, a rack hangs some animal offal in mid-air
orig: 在市场的摊贩前，半空中的一个架子挂起来一些动物内脏

caption: Animal offal hanging on the butcher stall, sausages hanging on the wall behind, cut meats in the freezer next to it, electric lights on the roof
orig: 肉摊上挂着的动物内脏，后面的墙上挂着香肠，旁边的冷柜里放着切成块的肉，屋顶有电灯

caption: Several blackberry fruits among the green leaves, some red and some black
orig: 在绿叶中结出的几个黑莓果实，有几个红色的有几个黑色的

caption: Wild blueberries in the garden, three clusters are red and three are black, with green leaves next to them
orig: 花园里的野蓝莓，有三簇是红色的，三簇是黑色的，旁边有绿叶

caption: Two men lying in a tent taking selfies at the camera
orig: 两个男士躺在帐篷中对着镜头自拍

caption: Two men were lying in a tent, one covered with a purple quilt and the other covered with a blue quilt. At the door of the tent were backpacks, bottled water and shoes, and outside the tent were woods.
orig: 两个男人躺在帐篷里，一个盖紫红色被子，一个盖蓝色被子，帐篷门口是背包，瓶装水和鞋子，帐篷外是树林

caption: Under the blue sky, the sun shines on people. A group of white soldiers in uniforms stand on the road next to the building. A few citizens stand on the outermost edge and look at them.
orig: 蓝蓝的天空下，阳光照耀到人们身上，建筑物旁的道路上站着一群身穿制服的白人士兵，最外围站着几个市民看着他们

caption: At the door of the building were a group of heavily armed soldiers in camouflage uniforms and three men in civilian clothes.
orig: 楼门口一群穿迷彩服全副武装的士兵，还有三个穿便服的男人

caption: There are tire marks on the concrete road in the mountain forest, and the road is lined with green plants.
orig: 山林里的混凝土路上面有轮胎的痕迹，道路两旁长满了绿植

caption: A flat artificial path in the forest, with lush vegetation on one side and stone walls on the other
orig: 森林里人工修成的平坦小路，一边是郁郁葱葱的植被，一边是石壁

caption: Under the sunlight, you can see a rushing river at the bottom of the two canyons and an iron bridge above.
orig: 阳光照耀下，可以看到两座峡谷底部是一条湍急的河流和上方的一座铁桥

caption: A ditch between two mountains. The stone walls on both sides of the ditch are very flat. The water flows far away from the ground. There is a bridge over the ditch. There are grasslands and green trees on the ground.
orig: 两处山地中间的沟渠，渠两边的石壁很平整，流水距离地面很远，渠上驾着一座桥，地面上是草地和绿树

caption: Seabirds flying in the sky can see the rolling waves below
orig: 天上飞的海鸟可以看到下面翻滚的海浪

caption: A group of seagulls are flying over the blue sea, the sky is filled with gray clouds, and there are high-rise buildings in the city in the distance
orig: 一群海鸥正在蔚蓝的海上飞翔，天空中布满灰色的云，远处有城市的高楼

caption: The afterglow of sunset shines on the sea
orig: 日落的余晖洒在海上

caption: The afterglow of the setting sun shines on the water, and the sun is about to set
orig: 落日的余晖洒在水面上，太阳即将落山

caption: Sailing boat on the sea in the sunset
orig: 晚霞中停留在海上的帆船

caption: The red sunset glow sets off the ships on the sea. There is a large ship with a towering mast.
orig: 红色的晚霞映衬下海上的船，有一条大船上有高耸的桅杆

caption: Someone is getting off the plane
orig: 有人在下飞机

caption: There is a large white plane parked with the word lufthansa written on it. There are two people standing on the boarding stairs. There are many cars under the plane.
orig: 停着的一架白色大飞机上写着lufthansa,有2个人站在登机楼梯上，飞机下面有很多车

caption: The photo shows two antique cars with many trophies on them.
orig: 照片上是两辆古董车上摆着很多个奖杯

caption: Two yellow classic cars
orig: 两辆黄色古典车

caption: There are two boys renovating the house
orig: 有两个男生在装修房子

caption: Two Asians are renovating a house, there is a blue cloth on the gray ground and various utensils are placed on the ground
orig: 两个亚洲人正在装修房子，灰色的地面上有一块蓝布，地上放着各种用具

caption: trees by the sea
orig: 靠海边的树木

caption: Olive trees next to the deep blue sea under the blue sky with mountains in the distance
orig: 蓝蓝的天空下深蓝色的大海旁边的橄榄树，远处有山

caption: There are a few young people camping by the lake preparing to take a boat
orig: 湖边有几个在露营的年轻人准备坐船

caption: There are many boats parked by the water, and many men are shirtless and wearing underwear, either standing on the shore or in the water, surrounded by trees and awnings.
orig: 水边停着很多小船，很多男人光着上半身穿着内裤，或站在岸边，或站在水中，周围有树和遮阳棚

caption: Standing on the beach, a child's hands move through the water
orig: 站在沙滩上小孩的手划过海水

caption: A pair of feet and a chubby hand on the beach, bronze skin, water on the beach
orig: 沙滩上的一双脚丫和一只小胖手，古铜色的皮肤，沙滩上有水

caption: pineapple
orig: 凤梨

caption: A growing pineapple with green leaves. The leaves under the pineapple are red.
orig: 一颗长着的凤梨，绿色的叶子，凤梨下的叶子红了

caption: A sandpiper on the marsh
orig: 沼泽上的一只滨鹬

caption: A snipe on the beach with water on the beach
orig: 沙滩上的一只鹬，沙滩上有水

caption: There is a boy posing for photos beside the stone fountain.
orig: 石雕喷水池边有个男生摆着姿势拍照

caption: A man in jeans stands next to a fountain. There is a tall black statue of a strong man in the fountain.
orig: 一个穿牛仔服的男人站在一处喷泉旁，喷泉里有一座黑色的高大的健壮的男人雕像

caption: Down from the green lawn is the sea
orig: 绿色草坪往下是海

caption: Looking at the sea from the foot of the mountain, the turquoise water, the shore is green moss, and the sky is filled with gray clouds
orig: 从山脚远望大海，碧绿的海水，岸边是绿色的青苔，天空中布满灰色的云

caption: A pink dog rose
orig: 一朵粉红色的犬蔷薇

caption: A pink wild rose growing with yellow stamens
orig: 生长的一朵粉色的野玫瑰，黄色的花蕊

caption: black and white skyscrapers
orig: 黑白照的摩天大楼

caption: Black and white photo of many tall buildings in the city with clouds in the sky
orig: 黑白照片，远眺城市的多栋高楼，天空中有云

caption: Italian made metal bicycle gear parts
orig: 意大利制造的金属自行车齿轮部件

caption: A disassembled bicycle gear
orig: 拆下来的一个自行车齿轮

caption: Fragmented ancient stone ruins on the mountain and a tractor in the distance
orig: 山上零碎的石造古遗址和远处一辆拖拉机

caption: Ancient city ruins scattered among green weeds on the mountain
orig: 山上绿色杂草间分布的古城遗址

caption: An old silver Ford car at the foot of the mountain with several people standing next to it
orig: 山脚下一辆旧银色福特车，旁边站着几个人

caption: A gray off-road vehicle splattered with mud is parked on the grass, with a shirtless man standing next to it, and two women and a man behind it
orig: 溅有泥的灰色越野车停在草地上，旁边站着一个赤膊男人，后面还有2个女人和1个男人

caption: Standing in the middle of the lake, it is a square cement building with a long pedestrian bridge in front of it.
orig: 立于湖中央，一所方方正正的水泥建筑，前方有一条很长的行人桥

caption: A gray building seen from a distance, surrounded by green trees, a river, street lights and a blue-gray sky next to the building
orig: 远看一栋灰色建筑，周围有绿树，建筑旁有河流、路灯，青灰色的天空

caption: An unknown animal in the depression of the sand sculpture
orig: 沙雕凹陷处一只不知名动物

caption: Close up view of stone carving
orig: 石刻的近景

caption: A white sailboat with two people sitting on the sea
orig: 海上一艘坐着两个人的白色风帆船

caption: A small boat sails on the river with two sails spread out. There are green trees on the other side of the river.
orig: 一条小船展开两张帆在河上行驶，河对岸有绿树

caption: Rough black and gray gradient plaid background
orig: 粗糙的黑灰白渐变色的格纹背景

caption: Monotonous picture of nothing in black and white
orig: 黑白色空无一物的单调画面

caption: Yellow roof plate with the word taksi engraved on the roof of a taxi
orig: 计程车车顶上刻有taksi字样的黄色车顶牌

caption: yellow taksi logo
orig: 黄色的taksi标识

caption: Next to the road, a Nestlé building made of iron frames is under construction.
orig: 在马路旁边，一所由铁架构成，正在施工中的雀巢建筑

caption: A building like a bird's nest is being built across the road, and there are many cars on the road
orig: 马路对面正在修建一栋像鸟巢一样的建筑，马路上有很多车

caption: Three wet, dead mackerel on a wooden board
orig: 木板上三条湿的，死了的鯖鱼

caption: There are three fish on the table
orig: 桌子上摆着三条鱼

caption: There is an orange lifebuoy with black words on the hull and a rope attached to it.
orig: 船身一个有黑字样，系着绳子的橘色救生圈

caption: Half view of orange lifebuoy with rope
orig: 带绳子的橘色救生圈半景

caption: Dry, winding majestic mountain landscape in the desert
orig: 沙漠中干枯，蜿蜒曲折的宏伟山脉景观

caption: Overlooking the winding roads in the mountains, the bare mountains
orig: 俯瞰群山峻岭中蜿蜒的公路，光秃秃的山

caption: Wooden signboard with yellow characters on a blue background warning people not to come into contact with wild animals
orig: 蓝底黄字，警告人们不要接触野生动物的木制告示牌

caption: Capital letters in yellow letters on a blue background remind tourists not to approach wild animals without permission.
orig: 蓝底黄字大写英文提醒游客不要擅自接近野生动物

caption: A black middle-aged male photographer holding a camera at the party
orig: 聚会中一位拿着相机的黑人中年男性摄影师

caption: A middle-aged man with white hair and dark skin wearing casual clothes smiles at the camera with a camera on his chest, and there is a bustling crowd of visitors behind him
orig: 一位白发黑皮肤穿着休闲的中年男人胸前挂着照相机面对镜头微笑，后面有熙熙攘攘的参观人群

caption: Family photo of eight adults and two children in front of a small wooden house in the forest
orig: 森林里一所小木屋前，八个大人，两个小孩的家庭照

caption: A family of 10 faces the camera with 2 small children standing outside a reddish-brown wooden farm house, surrounded by green trees, grass and mountains
orig: 一个10口之家站在红褐色木头农家房子外面面对镜头，有2个小孩，周围是绿树、碧草和群山

caption: A yellow wooden door in the middle of a white wall under sunlight
orig: 阳光照耀下白墙中间的一扇黄色的木制大门

caption: A yellow wooden door on a white wall looks like a garage doorway
orig: 白墙上的一处黄色木门，看起来像一个车库的门口

caption: There are three workers wearing orange reflective vests and yellow safety helmets standing in the underground tunnel. The one in the middle is smiling towards the camera, and the other two are facing away from the camera.
orig: 地下隧道里站着三位穿着橙色反光背心、带着黄色安全帽的工人，中间的这位面向镜头微笑，其他两位背向镜头

caption: There are three engineers in the tunnel wearing orange safety suits and yellow helmets. Two of them have their backs to the camera, and one of them is smiling towards the camera. They seem to be building a subway. There are lights everywhere on the top of the tunnel.
orig: 隧道里的3个穿橘黄色安全服戴黄色安全帽的工程师，2个背对镜头，1个面对镜头微笑，好像在修地铁，随处隧道顶上有光

caption: An old man with white hair is standing on the stage giving a speech. His overall image is enlarged on the big screen. Others are sitting on the conference table in the lower left corner.
orig: 舞台上一位白发老人正站在做演讲，大屏幕上放大他的整体形象，左下角的会议桌上坐着其他人

caption: There was an expert in a suit and glasses speaking at the venue. His image was displayed on the big screen. There were two experts in suits and ties sitting next to him.
orig: 会场有个穿西装戴眼镜的专家在讲话，大屏幕上显示着他的影像，旁边的坐席上还有2名西装革履的专家

caption: A yellow table contains typical Japanese food such as salmon sashimi, vegetables, and rice on a black plate.
orig: 一张黄色桌子上摆着一个黑色盘子装着的三文鱼刺身、蔬菜、包饭等典型的日式食物

caption: Japanese sushi, sashimi, vegetables on black plate
orig: 黑色盘子里放的日本寿司、生鱼片、蔬菜

caption: There is a woman on the left and two men on the right. The three of them took a selfie smiling at the camera. The man on the far right puts his hand on the shoulder of the man in the middle. There are paintings hanging on the wall behind them.
orig: 左边是一位女士，右边是两位男士，三个人一起面向镜头微笑的自拍照，其中最右边男士的手放在中间男士的肩膀上，他们身后的墙壁上挂着画

caption: Three Vietnamese people are smiling at the camera indoors. A man and a woman are sitting. The man in a red shirt is standing next to another man. There is a painting on the wall. The photo is a bit backlit.
orig: 室内3个越南人面对镜头微笑，一男一女坐着，穿红色衬衫的男子站在另一个男子旁边，墙上有一副画，照片整体有点背光

caption: Cooked spicy fried clams in a white disk on a white table
orig: 一张白色桌子上的白色磁盘里装着烹饪好的辣炒蛤蜊

caption: Plate of fried clams with green and red chili peppers on a white plate, opposite a glass cup, water, white plate, fork
orig: 白盘里的一盘炒蛤蜊，里面有绿色和红色的辣椒，对面有玻璃杯、水、白盘、叉子

caption: Standing upstairs and looking down, there are vehicles coming and going on a wide road. There is a long queue of vehicles on the left side of the road. There are buildings on the left side of the road and a piece of grass on the right side.
orig: 站在楼上向下看，一条宽阔的马路上来来往往的车辆，其中左侧的道路的车辆排着很长的队伍，道路左侧是建筑物，右侧是一片草地

caption: Vehicles driving on the street, straight street, crowded lanes on the left, a few sparse cars on the right, high-rise buildings in the distance, buildings on the left of the road, green trees and lawns on the right
orig: 街上行驶的车辆，笔直的街道，左边挤满车道，右边稀稀拉拉的几辆车，远处有高楼大厦，路左边是楼房，路右有绿树草坪

caption: Residential houses on the seaside are illuminated by the sun, and you can see the blue water and rolling mountains in the distance.
orig: 阳光照耀下海边的居民住宅，向远处望去是一片蓝蓝的海水和起伏的山脉

caption: An ancient city ruins on the seaside under the blue sky, azure water, mountains in the distance, the incomplete walls of the ancient city nearby, and a small white dome building, many with chimneys on the roofs, and green trees with exposed branches on both sides
orig: 蓝天下海边的一处古城遗址，蔚蓝的海水，远处有山，近处是古城残缺的墙壁，还有一白色的小型圆顶建筑，很多房顶有烟囱，两边有绿树露出树枝

caption: In front of the gate of a typical European-style building under a dark cloudy sky, the minaret on the right seems to tower into the clouds.
orig: 乌云密布的天空下一栋典型欧式建筑大门前，右边的尖塔感觉尖耸入云

caption: The entrance of a mosque has an arched door with Arabic characters on a green background and yellow characters on the lintel. The tall minaret looks a bit old.
orig: 一座清真寺门口，拱形的门，门楣上有绿底黄字阿拉伯文，高高的尖塔，看起来有点旧

caption: At night, the lights of rows of streetlights on the roadside illuminate the buildings
orig: 夜晚时分，马路边上一排排路灯的灯光照耀着建筑物

caption: A winding road by the sea at night, with street lights, coconut trees, and low buildings on the right, and the messy stones of the seawall on the left
orig: 夜晚海边蜿蜒的小路，右边有路灯、椰树、低矮的小楼，左边是海堤杂乱的石头

caption: A herd of black goats stands in a narrow passage between rural huts under sunlight, with people standing behind them
orig: 阳光照耀下，农村小屋之间狭窄的通道里有一群黑山羊，后面站着人

caption: Two children are driving a group of brown sheep in a dilapidated alley, including large sheep and lambs.
orig: 破巷子里2个小孩正在赶一群棕褐色的羊，有大羊和羊羔

caption: Close-up of yellow corn kernels on the cob under sunlight
orig: 阳光照耀下玉米棒上黄色的玉米粒特写

caption: Close-up shot of a stick of yellow corn, the kernels are shiny and the background is blurred
orig: 近拍一棒黄玉米，玉米粒油亮油亮的，背景虚化

caption: Standing in the open space and looking at the green space, mountains and sky in the distance, the sky and the snow on the top of the mountain are all white.
orig: 站在空地上看向远处的绿地、山脉和天空的景色，天空和山顶的积雪都是白色的

caption: Mountain scenery under blue sky and white clouds, with winding roads, snow and green trees on the top of the mountain, and green grassland at the bottom of the mountain
orig: 蓝天白云下的山间风光，有蜿蜒的道路，山顶有积雪、有绿树，山下有绿色草地

caption: Several men in sportswear are sitting on a felled branch in the woods and resting in the sun, with their equipment next to them
orig: 阳光照耀下几位穿着运动服的男士坐在树林里被砍伐过的树枝上休息，旁边放着他们的装备

caption: Three hiking men were sitting in the woods to rest, all carrying large backpacks. The man in red was sitting on a dead tree, one was sitting on a stone mountain, and the other was sitting on the ground. They were surrounded by trees.
orig: 3个徒步旅行的男人坐在树林里休息，都背着大大的背包，穿红衣服的哪入坐在一根枯木上，一个坐在石头山，一个坐在地上，周围都是树

caption: A couple of good friends taking a selfie while sitting at the kitchen table at home and looking up at the camera
orig: 几个好朋友在家里厨房的桌子旁坐着并抬头看向镜头自拍

caption: A group of young men and women are queuing up in the house. A woman in a white shirt is holding a camera and smiling at the camera. The man in a gray hoodie next to her is looking up at the camera. There are glasses and cans on the table, and there is water and water on the stove behind. Drinks, soups, cups, etc., with people on both sides
orig: 一群年轻男女在屋里开排队，一名穿白衬衫女子手拿照相机面对镜头微笑，旁边的灰色帽衫男子正抬头看镜头，桌上有玻璃杯和罐头，后面的灶台上有水、饮料、汤、杯子等，两边还有人

caption: A pale green lake under the sunlight, with a green forest in the distance
orig: 阳光照耀下一片淡绿色的湖水，远处是一片绿色的树林

caption: rippling blue lake water
orig: 碧波荡漾的湖水

caption: A logo on a white background, with 100 written in a yellow box that looks like a stack of paper dripping with blood. Below is blood dripping on the palm of the hand, and at the bottom is a paragraph of foreign letters.
orig: 在一块白色背景下的标识，一个黄色框中类似一叠滴血纸上写着100，下面是血滴落在手掌里，最下面是一段外文字母

caption: The sign has a square with one hundred written on it and a red color dripping onto one hand.

orig: 一个穿绿色衣的男生在看着大象们洗泥土浴

caption: In an elephant farm surrounded by woods, a man is looking at five elephants. One is drinking water from a puddle, another is drinking water from a blue bucket, and the other three are gathered in the corner.
orig: 树林围绕的象群饲养场，一位男士正在看着五只大象，一只在水坑内吸水一只在喝蓝色桶内的水，其他三只聚集在角落

caption: Under the bridge is the surging river
orig: 大桥下是滔滔的河水

caption: A close up view of Chichibu Bridge in Japan with pedestrians on the bridge
orig: 日本秩父桥的一段近景，桥上有行人

caption: a bird on a branch
orig: 一只鸟在树枝上

caption: Close-up of a sunbird on a branch
orig: 树枝上的一只太阳鸟特写

caption: The lights of the bridge crossing the river are all on
orig: 渡江的大桥的灯光都亮起了

caption: At night, street lights are lit on the stone pier bridge. There are lights and light strips dotted on the arched bridge hole. There are boats on the lake and houses in the distance.
orig: 夜幕下的石墩架桥上亮起了路灯，拱形桥洞上有点缀的灯光和灯带，湖面上有小船，远处是房屋

caption: Close-up of poster from the perspective of old photo
orig: 旧照片视角下的海报特写

caption: A rusty old poster, the content cannot be seen clearly, there are some red forehead marks, and the words 15.12 are written below
orig: 一张生锈的旧海报，看不清内容，有一些红色额痕迹，下面有15.12字样

caption: A bear bento made of purple rice in a yellow lunch box
orig: 黄色的饭盒里面装着的用紫色的米做成的小熊便当

caption: Food in yellow lunch box on pink tablecloth, purple bear made of rice, with egg rolls, shrimp, nuts, etc.
orig: 粉色的桌布上黄色饭盒里的食物，有用米饭做的紫色小熊，配有蛋卷、虾、坚果等

caption: From the perspective of standing on the road and looking into the distance, there are many white clouds in the sky. Across the road is a tall cylindrical building surrounded by two buildings.
orig: 站在马路上向远处看的视角，天空中有很多白云，马路对面是两栋建筑围起来的圆柱形的高楼

caption: A cylindrical skyscraper under the blue sky with green glass and some low buildings below. There are lawns and trees next to it. Several people are standing on the roadside. Someone is walking across the crosswalk. There are gray clouds in the sky.
orig: 蓝天下一栋圆柱形摩天大楼，绿色的玻璃，下方还有一些低矮的楼，旁边有草坪和树，路边站着几个人，有人正从人行横道走过，天上有灰云

caption: A military helicopter is flying over the city
orig: 在城市上空一辆军用直升机正在飞行

caption: A military helicopter in the gray mid-air with many buildings in the distance
orig: 灰色半空中一架军用直升飞机，远处有很多楼房

caption: In cloudy weather, standing on the mountains and looking into the distance, there is a field of green plants and continuous mountains.
orig: 多云天气下，站在山脉上看向远处，是一片绿色的植物和连绵的山脉

caption: The scenery on the mountain under the blue sky and white clouds, the green grass and some small trees planted
orig: 蓝天白云下山上的景色，碧绿的草地，栽着一些小树

caption: In the square under the blue sky, two soldiers are guarding a huge multi-person stone monument, with city buildings behind it
orig: 蓝天之下的广场上，两个军人正在守卫巨大的多人石雕纪念碑，后方是城市建筑物

caption: Under the blue sky and white clouds, a stone monument towers into the night sky. There is a green statue of a human figure on the top of the stone monument. There are also human statues on the base of the stone monument. There are two soldiers standing under the stone monument. There are many buildings behind it.
orig: 蓝天白云下一座石碑耸入云宵，石碑顶部有一座绿色的人物雕像，碑座上也有人物雕像，石碑下面站着两名军人，后面有很多楼房

caption: Two people are having fun in the blue swimming pool, and they can still see rows of deck chairs and green trees next to them.
orig: 在蓝色游泳池里两个人正在有用，还能看到旁边的一排排躺椅和绿树

caption: The hotel's swimming pool has blue water. There is a man and a little girl swimming in it. There are many white lounge chairs on the shore in the distance, a few people, and coconut trees.
orig: 酒店的游泳池，碧蓝的池水，里面有一个男人和一个小姑娘在游泳，远处岸边有许多白色躺椅，有几个人，还有椰树

caption: A black backpack is placed on a beige table in the room
orig: 一个黑色的双肩包被放在房间里一张米色的桌子上

caption: There is a black backpack standing on the yellow desk, a black phone next to it, and a simple painting on the far wall
orig: 黄色办公桌上立着一个黑色的背包，旁边有一部黑色电话，远处墙上有一幅简易画

caption: Against the background of the sky, a square reflector hangs on the trunk of a large tree, inside which a pedestrian can be seen walking on the track
orig: 在天空背景下，一棵大树的树干上挂着一块方形的反光镜，能看到里面有一个行人走在轨道上

caption: A mirror on a tree on a cloudy day with some red dotted lines on the white edge and a man in jeans standing on the rails
orig: 阴天树上的一面镜子，白边上有一些红色虚线，镜子里有个穿牛仔裤的人站在铁轨上

caption: In the conference room, a woman wearing a white suit and long hair holds a remote control in her left hand and makes a gesture with her right hand. Behind her is a projector slide that is playing.
orig: 在会议室里一位身着白色西装、披着长发的女性左手拿着遥控器，右手做出一的姿势，她的身后是正在播放的投影仪幻灯片

caption: A Korean woman wearing a white suit and a pearl necklace is standing and giving a lecture. She is holding a remote control in her right hand and pointing to the sky with her left hand. There is a photo with Korean characters on the projector display behind her.
orig: 一名韩国女士穿着白色西服带戴珍珠项链站着讲课，右手拿着遥控器，左手指天，后面的投影仪显示屏上有一张带韩国字的照片

caption: In the corner of the room is a large box of figurines.
orig: 在房间角落里摆着一个很大盒子装着的手办

caption: A pinball machine with golden game patterns on it, a printer on the left, and paper, books, file boxes, etc. below the printer
orig: 弹球机，上面有金灿灿的游戏图案，左边有打印机，打印机下面有纸、书、文件盒等

caption: Close-up of a donut sprinkled with nuts on a white plastic bag
orig: 白色塑料袋上的一个洒满坚果的甜甜圈特写

caption: A donut sprinkled with icing, seemingly on a plastic sheet
orig: 一个撒着糖衣的炸面圈，好像是放在塑料布上

caption: An ingredient list written in a foreign language with green fonts on a white background.
orig: 一张外文写的配料表的组成说明，白色的背景绿色的字体

caption: A piece of white paper with green text on the food packaging pattern, with brand, address, nutritional information table, phone number, email address, production date, etc.
orig: 一张白纸绿字食品包装图案，上面有品牌，地址、营养成分表、电话、邮箱、生产日期等

caption: A closed white helmet stained with purple
orig: 一个关闭着的白色头盔上面被紫色污染

caption: A white helmet, with pink paint falling off it in patches, with blue sky and green trees in the distance
orig: 一个白色头盔，上面就像掉了粉色颜料，一片一片的，远处有蓝天盒绿树

caption: Under the light of a fruit stall, various fruits are placed in a pile alone on a white tablecloth. A man is looking into the distance with his hands raised and pulling the string.
orig: 在一个水果摊的灯光照耀下，白色的桌布上各种水果独自摆成一摞，一位男士双手举起拉着线正看向远方

caption: A covered fruit stall with apples, grapes, oranges and other fruits on display, with a man sitting in the middle holding the roped fruits above with his hands raised
orig: 带顶棚的水果摊，摆着苹果、葡萄、橙子等各种水果，中间坐着一个男人举起双手抓着上面的绳子水果
